title: EN05S Tattoo Needle Cartridges Round Liner/ RL 20 PCS
desc: With the help of EN05S needle cartridges, you’ll have a new experience while tattooing that the surfaces are filled consistently, reliably, and most importantly, more efficiently. EN05Stattoo needle will also give your customer a completely different tattoo experience – less trauma for their skin.Combined with our new arrival machine CNC S1 Wireless Tattoo Machine Brushless Motor, open up your creative tattoo works.Features/nA new experience for tattooists and the tattooists’ customers – ink flow consistency and less trauma on the skin./nSoft silicone rebound, perfectly matched to the Faulhaber motor, with low resistance and no damage to the motor./nTransparent tip for easy observation of INK./nNeedle made of surgical stainless steel. 100% EO Gas Sterilized and individually packaged, Medical-grade plastic shell./nSterile and environmentally friendly packaging./nDecades of tattoo needle manufacture experience, craft needle suitable for ultra-precise, and omnidirectional work.Parameters/nConfiguration: Round Linner/RL Cartridge/nNeedle Diameter: 0.30 mm(starts with 10) – 0.35mm (starts with 12)/nBox Quantity: 20 cartridges/nTransparent Tip/nSingle-mould casing/nMedical-grade plastic tips/nSafety membrane/nCompatible with cartridge grips and most brand machines on the market.
